<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Action Required: Low Product Quantity</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #ff4757;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f1f3f5;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #868e96;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #ff4757;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #e03e50;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            Action Required: Low Product Quantity
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear {{sellerName}},</p>
            <p>We hope this email finds you well. This is to inform you that some products in your inventory have
                reached low stock levels.</p>
            <p>To avoid disruptions in sales, please review your stock and restock the following items as soon as
                possible:</p>
            <ul>
                {{#each lowStockProducts}}
                <li><strong>{{this.productName}}</strong>: Only <strong>{{this.quantity}}</strong> left in stock.</li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
            <p>For more details, you can visit your inventory dashboard by clicking the button below:</p>
            <a href="{{inventoryDashboardLink}}" class="button">View Inventory</a>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            &copy; {{year}} ShopXIndia. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>